highlights.text: Diego Mitre has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “To the Infinity Castle - Muzan vs Hashira Theme (from "Demon Slayer") - Cover” is the highest at #2.
“おつかれSUMMER” by HALCALI has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 114 days straight.
“MALVADO DE VAPO” by xccvdxz and Y3LLAVISION is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 20 spots at #40.
“Akaza's Past Full Theme (Demon Slayer Infinity Castle Movie: Akaza's Return)” by Ashif N is the highest new entry on Viral Songs South Korea at #29.
